111
00:10:11,580 --> 00:10:13,840
That was your fault!

112
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:15,420
That's called self-defense.

113
00:10:15,420 --> 00:10:17,120
But still, you're a police officer!

114
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:19,520
Back then, I was an elementary student!

115
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:23,900
Because of that, I became a police officer, so I could take down the bad guys!

116
00:10:25,110 --> 00:10:29,040
Why did you do it? To get revenge on me?

117
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:33,410
