120
00:10:38,450 --> 00:10:40,410
What are you talking about?

121
00:10:40,410 --> 00:10:42,490
Who killed whom?

122
00:10:42,490 --> 00:10:45,510
I might commit fraud but not murder!

123
00:10:45,510 --> 00:10:47,250
You killed Kwon Bo Yeon!

124
00:10:47,250 --> 00:10:50,220
The Choco Pie and vitamin candy are unmistakably your M.O.

125
00:10:50,220 --> 00:10:54,370
