128
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:04,580
What's with this mood?

129
00:11:04,580 --> 00:11:07,400
I didn't do it. I didn't kill her!

130
00:11:07,400 --> 00:11:09,220
A murderer should use honorifics!

131
00:11:09,220 --> 00:11:14,810
Wow, this is crazy! It wasn't me!

132
00:11:16,310 --> 00:11:18,570
You have the right to remain silent.

133
