Real Estate asked me for a favor, so I went in with him.

148
00:12:17,780 --> 00:12:22,120
The can was laying there, and it scared me so much!

149
00:12:22,790 --> 00:12:28,030
I felt so bad toward that lady. What do I do, Dae Seong?

150
00:12:28,030 --> 00:12:32,400
Mom, you don't need to be scared. I caught 5,000 Won.

151
