5,000 Won? What are you talking about all of a sudden?

152
00:12:36,640 --> 00:12:38,970
- 5,000 Won was the culprit. 
 - What?

153
00:12:40,160 --> 00:12:45,190
Kwon Bo Yeon, and now Lee Kyeong Ah...

154
00:12:45,190 --> 00:12:47,890
She was killed with the canned peaches, right? Was she struck in the head?

155
00:12:47,890 --> 00:12:50,390
Ahn Dae Seong, you don't need to worry about this anymore, so—

156
