5,000 Won bought canned peaches and a can opener at our store.

157
00:12:53,250 --> 00:12:56,520
The Catholic church volunteer bought them for him and took them to him at the hospital, and today—

158
00:12:56,520 --> 00:13:00,490
5,000 Won was at our store?!

159
00:13:03,930 --> 00:13:08,500
Geez, why are you bringing me up here?

160
00:13:09,420 --> 00:13:12,390
That's the nunchuck grandpa!

161
00:13:12,390 --> 00:13:16,540
So... the nunchuck grandpa is 5,000 Won.

162
00:13:16,540 --> 00:13:19,440
He was hiding out in our neighborhood for 10 years, but we didn't know.

163
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:21,120
Stand up straight!

164
