216
00:17:36,690 --> 00:17:39,560
- How dare you?! 
 - Please stop.

217
00:17:39,560 --> 00:17:43,950
- Stop! 
 - Go ahead and hit me! Kill me!

218
00:17:45,950 --> 00:17:49,880
Are you having a neighborhood meeting at the crime scene? How will we catch the culprit this way?

