01:02:47,980 --> 01:02:50,980
♫   To look over   ♫

700
01:02:50,980 --> 01:02:55,210
  You can't trust anybody. I think it's a good idea to rule out the mart's employees.

701
01:02:55,210 --> 01:02:56,060
 What?

702
01:02:56,060 --> 01:02:57,860
♫   You've already gone so far   ♫

