01:02:59,790 --> 01:03:03,830
 It's a far more certain motive than I had thought.  Gong San is very ambitious.

705
01:03:03,830 --> 01:03:06,610
  Sir, there are rumors that you're the criminal.

706
01:03:06,610 --> 01:03:08,250
 That it's a murderer's store.

707
01:03:08,250 --> 01:03:10,880
  Why are you asking the wrong person instead of catching the criminal?

708
01:03:10,880 --> 01:03:17,670
 The spot where the shoe fell could be the actual crime scene and Yool could be the eyewitness.

709
01:03:17,670 --> 01:03:18,880
♫  Everything  ♫

710
01:03:18,880 --> 01:03:20,790
  Be careful of Fish.

711
01:03:20,790 --> 01:03:22,190
♫  Why, why  ♫

712
01:03:22,190 --> 01:03:23,330
  Yool could be in danger.

713
01:03:23,330 --> 01:03:24,200
  Yool!

714
01:03:24,200 --> 01:03:26,300
  Do you know of any places she could have gone?

715
01:03:26,300 --> 01:03:28,190
♫  There's no such thing as a secret  ♫

